# 📊 Excel Bike Sales Dashboard Project

This repository contains a Sales Dashboard project created using **Microsoft Excel** as part of my hands-on learning in data analysis.

## 🎯 Objective
To build a professional, interactive sales dashboard in Excel that summarizes key sales metrics by region, product, and date.

## 📹 Tutorial Credit
This project was completed by following a step-by-step tutorial by **Alex Freberg** on his YouTube channel **[Alex The Analyst](https://www.youtube.com/@AlexTheAnalyst)**.

🔗 [Watch the video here](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=opJgMj1IUrc&list=PLUaB-1hjhk8Hyd5NiPQ9CND82vNodlFF5&index=7)

## 💼 Skills Practiced
- Data Cleaning and Formatting
- Pivot Tables and Pivot Charts
- Dynamic Dashboards using Slicers
- Excel formulas: `SUMIFS`, `COUNTIFS`, `VLOOKUP`, `IF`, and more
- Conditional Formatting and Layout Design

## 🧠 Key Learnings
- How to structure raw data for dashboarding
- How to visualize insights using Excel tools
- How to enhance dashboard interactivity using slicers and conditional visuals

## 📁 Project Files
- `sales_data.xlsx` – cleaned sample dataset used
- `dashboard_screenshot.png` – preview of the dashboard (optional)
- `README.md` – project description

## 🙏 Acknowledgement
Full credit to **Alex Freberg** (Alex The Analyst) for the original tutorial and guidance.

